  "detailed_description": "You are a fish.<br><br>Armed with your grappling hook-equipped sniper rifle, go on the ultimate <i>krilling</i> spree in <strong>Hook Line & Sniper</strong>! In this fast-paced arcade shooter, rack up points by mastering your arsenal and maximizing your style. Battle foes in and above the sea, show no mercy, and prove who’s the REAL apex predator!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143190/extras/95cfe06787a3bb41d9b06dacb3b3cf6b.webp?t=1752626210\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143190/extras/ab97a92865887b3726be7a78c3147b74.poster.avif?t=1752626210\" width=318 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143190/extras/ab97a92865887b3726be7a78c3147b74.webm?t=1752626210\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143190/extras/ab97a92865887b3726be7a78c3147b74.mp4?t=1752626210\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Grapple into the sky or divebomb into enemies<br></li><li>Build your arsenal as you progress<br></li><li>Quickly swap between weapons on the fly, boosting moment-to-moment gameplay<br></li><li>It’s badass</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143190/extras/795ed63fdf8b0097eb226a3772b05f5c.webp?t=1752626210\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143190/extras/bd261b36a3f69feb1d776e8b26d5ddb2.poster.avif?t=1752626210\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143190/extras/bd261b36a3f69feb1d776e8b26d5ddb2.webm?t=1752626210\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143190/extras/bd261b36a3f69feb1d776e8b26d5ddb2.mp4?t=1752626210\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Easy to pick up, with copious opportunities for skill expression<br></li><li>Take on several unique challenges<br></li><li>Overflow the style meter in your own fishy way</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143190/extras/c1ea9a97cc6c4af62812b87bd583e075.webp?t=1752626210\" width=600 height=60 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143190/extras/a2becb508b544974cafadfe53d1dfd2a.poster.avif?t=1752626210\" width=318 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143190/extras/a2becb508b544974cafadfe53d1dfd2a.webm?t=1752626210\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143190/extras/a2becb508b544974cafadfe53d1dfd2a.mp4?t=1752626210\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Traverse beautiful ocean scenery<br></li><li>Battle all that the sea has to offer, from exploding pufferfish to flying pirate <i>shrimps</i><br></li><li>Watch out for hazards, or else you’re Fish Finished!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "You are a fish.<br><br>Armed with your grappling hook-equipped sniper rifle, go on the ultimate <i>krilling</i> spree in <strong>Hook Line & Sniper</strong>! In this fast-paced arcade shooter, rack up points by mastering your arsenal and maximizing your style. Battle foes in and above the sea, show no mercy, and prove who’s the REAL apex predator!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143190/extras/95cfe06787a3bb41d9b06dacb3b3cf6b.webp?t=1752626210\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143190/extras/ab97a92865887b3726be7a78c3147b74.poster.avif?t=1752626210\" width=318 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143190/extras/ab97a92865887b3726be7a78c3147b74.webm?t=1752626210\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143190/extras/ab97a92865887b3726be7a78c3147b74.mp4?t=1752626210\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Grapple into the sky or divebomb into enemies<br></li><li>Build your arsenal as you progress<br></li><li>Quickly swap between weapons on the fly, boosting moment-to-moment gameplay<br></li><li>It’s badass</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143190/extras/795ed63fdf8b0097eb226a3772b05f5c.webp?t=1752626210\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143190/extras/bd261b36a3f69feb1d776e8b26d5ddb2.poster.avif?t=1752626210\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamst